Facial expression Recognition.

This is a facial expression recognition project which tell the face expression like sad, happy etc and also display a corresponding emoji. In this I used OpenCV to detect our face and a deep learning model that is built on FER2013 dataset which predict some result then it is mapped with the corresponding emoji. I also uses Python Tkinter GUI to display the camera window and emoji at the same place.
